simulator lang=spectre
global 0
ahdl_include "dac_restore_6bit_1p8.va"
Vclk (clk 0) vsource type=pulse val0=0 val1=1.8 delay=0.35n period=1n width=0.35n rise=20p fall=20p
Vd1 (d1 0) vsource type=pwl wave=[0 0 2.0n 0 2.05n 1.8 4.0n 1.8]
Vd2 (d2 0) vsource type=pwl wave=[0 0 1.0n 0 1.05n 1.8 2.0n 1.8 2.05n 0 3.0n 0 3.05n 1.8 4.0n 1.8]
Vd3 (d3 0) vsource type=pwl wave=[0 0 2.0n 0 2.05n 1.8 3.0n 1.8 3.05n 1.8 4.0n 1.8]
Vd4 (d4 0) vsource type=pwl wave=[0 0 1.0n 0 1.05n 1.8 2.0n 1.8 2.05n 0 3.0n 0 3.05n 1.8 4.0n 1.8]
Vd5 (d5 0) vsource type=pwl wave=[0 0 2.0n 0 2.05n 1.8 3.0n 1.8 3.05n 1.8 4.0n 1.8]
Vd6 (d6 0) vsource type=pwl wave=[0 0 1.0n 0 1.05n 1.8 2.0n 1.8 2.05n 0 3.0n 0 3.05n 1.8 4.0n 1.8]
XDUT (d1 d2 d3 d4 d5 d6 clk vout) dac_restore_6bit_1p8
tran tran stop=3.8n maxstep=5p
save clk d1 d2 d3 d4 d5 d6 vout
